Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,到底哪里笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明夸了她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,明明为伊波的恋爱打气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我又没做错事 应该也没说错话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要在意 一切照常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,照常 照常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小…宗
