Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.53,OPC,,0,0,0,,变得狂野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.90,OPC,,0,0,0,,向着恋爱的秘境 (Go baby NEW-NEW)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.54,OPC,,0,0,0,,进发 (Go,baby NEW-WAY NEW-WAY)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:38.57,OPC,,0,0,0,,黄昏之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:40.99,OPC,,0,0,0,,不管何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:45.55,OPC,,0,0,0,,都让我们在一起吧
